Water of Life

While not as skilled in the healing arts as a cleric,
a druid does have a fair amount of knowledge of the
healing arts.  This spell is their simplest magical
tool to that end:  a spray of enchanted water to
literally wash wounds away.

Command: life <target> (defaults to caster)
Base Cost: 10 + 2 X guild level SP
Base Recovery: short
Base Effect: heal (moderate)
Base Duration: instant
Guild Level: 2
